column_description:
the id of the customer
Maps to customer(customer_id)

the id of the address
Maps to address(address_id)
the id of the address status
value_description:
commonsense evidence:
A customer may have several addresses. If a customer has several addresses, the address that the status_id = 1 is the customer's current address that is in use. The other addresses with 2 as status_id is abandoned addresses.
